snippet.title: Brazen Blaze - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Brazen Blaze is a 3v3 Smack & Shoot VR Action with a heavy focus on close quarter melee combat. Choose from a variety of characters with unique skills to destroy whatever lies in your path to achieve victory.
